reviewText: I think this is a great collection. I would recommend it if you like paranormal movies and suspense you will enjoy this collection.
Great films.  I love all 4 of them.  I already had one of them, but it was worth the price to get the other 3.  I'll watch these over and over again.
A nice set of four scary films if your a horror movie fan. I like the bag for the buck

Well 2 out of 4 aren't bad I suppose. I wish they weren't all in same case as I bought them as a gift 4 myself & friend.
Intended 2 send 1 or 2 not knowing they were all in one case.

I love to pop popcorn and put on a scary movie when it is raining outside. These movies fill the bill. I  enjoyed them, They were in great condition to be older movies. I will buy from this seller again.

Bought for haunting in Connecticut mainly

Received a four film collection with
American Haunting, Haunting in Connecticut,The Eye, The Others.. a bit strange

Didn't receive Soul Survivors(Another reason I bought this collection)
 I prefer The Others over riding the bullet as I already own it
All the movies I was thinking about. Interesting background and historical info
I really only bought it for a couple of the movies on there but couldn't pass up the deal for the set.  Haunting of Connecticut is really great plus bonus movies?  Ummm yes please.
4 great movies .Great packaging. Great quality. Great price. Very satisfied!
I like old scary movies. These movies are unusual but I like them.
Fun and high suspense movies with a couple of fun twists.
My main focus was for the An American Haunting but after watching the others I thought they were all great.
